COLD UNTIL AUGUST REMEMBER Starting tomorrow at  am  hours we will experience the APHELION PHENOMENON The Earth will be very far from the Sun  We cannot see the phenomenon but we CAN feel its impact It will last until the month of August We will have cold weather MORE COLD THAN EVER which will lead to flu cough difficulty breathing etc We must increase immunity by using many vitamins and supplements to make our health strong The distance from the Earth to the Sun is  light minutes or  million km The Aphelion phenomenon takes us  million km from the Sun that is  further The air will become colder our bodies are not used to this temperature there is a big difference We must maintain our health conditions as much as possible it does not matter if it is cloudy or sunny the increase in cold will be the same  Please share this information with all your family and friends As many people as possible so that they can also take precautions LETS TAKE CARE OF OURSELVES
